        <updateDate>2023-08-16T10:33:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Pay for Congressional Recklessness Act</b></p> <p>This bill withholds congressional salaries and restricts the use of federal funds for travel by Members of Congress and executive branch employees while a continuing resolution (CR) is in effect. For the 118th Congress and subsequent Congresses, the bill also reduces congressional salaries by 1% for each day that a CR is in effect. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
